title: Missing CDC doctor was passed up for promotion: police
text:
Missing CDC doctor was passed up for promotion: police 8:34am EST - 01:49 
Atlanta police say Timothy Cunningham, the CDC doctor who has been missing for more than two weeks, didn't get the promotion he wanted before he disappeared. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
